11#ifndef COMMON_VIDEO_H265_H265_VPS_PARSER_H_
12#define COMMON_VIDEO_H265_H265_VPS_PARSER_H_
13
14#include "absl/types/optional.h"
15
16namespace rtc {
17class BitBuffer;
18}
19
20namespace webrtc {
21
22// A class for parsing out sequence parameter set (VPS) data from an H265 NALU.
23class H265VpsParser {
24 public:
25 // The parsed state of the VPS. Only some select values are stored.
26 // Add more as they are actually needed.
27 struct VpsState {
28 VpsState();
29
30 uint32_t id = 0;
31 };
32
33 // Unpack RBSP and parse VPS state from the supplied buffer.
34 static absl::optional<VpsState> ParseVps(const uint8_t* data, size_t length);
35
36 protected:
37 // Parse the VPS state, for a bit buffer where RBSP decoding has already been
38 // performed.
39 static absl::optional<VpsState> ParseInternal(rtc::BitBuffer* bit_buffer);
40};
41
42} // namespace webrtc
43#endif // COMMON_VIDEO_H265_H265_VPS_PARSER_H_
